			<item>
				<title>Collection</title>
				<link>http://localhost:8080/collection/</link>
				<pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:8080/collection/</guid>
				<description>&lt;div class=&#34;coll-header&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h2&gt;Our Collection&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;coll-sub&#34;&gt;Every Sensible Bag is designed with purpose — discover the piece that fits your life.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;coll-grid&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;coll-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;coll-img-wrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:8080/img/product-01.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;The Elongated Shoulder Bag&#34; /&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;coll-info&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;The Elongated Shoulder Bag&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;A refined silhouette with side drawstrings and custom gold hardware. Rich brown suede with signature double-stitched detailing.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;coll-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;coll-img-wrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:8080/img/product-02.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;The Structured Satchel&#34; /&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;coll-info&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;The Structured Satchel&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Trapezoidal satchel with polished gold turn-lock closure. Smooth leather accents complement the textured suede body.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;coll-card&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;coll-img-wrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:8080/img/product-03.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;The Classic Tote&#34; /&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;coll-info&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;The Classic Tote&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Generous trapezoidal tote with double shoulder straps. Features a leather luggage tag and gold-tone protective feet.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>Company Profile</title>
				<link>http://localhost:8080/about/</link>
				<pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:8080/about/</guid>
				<description>&lt;!-- ═══════════ HERO 区块 ═══════════ --&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;ab-hero&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:8080/img/factory-gate.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Sensible Bag Headquarters&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;ab-hero-overlay&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;ab-label&#34;&gt;Est. 2013 · Dongguan, China&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h1&gt;We Make Bags That Work&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;A vertically integrated handbag manufacturer trusted by the world&#39;s most discerning fashion brands. From sketch to shipment — all under one roof.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- ═══════════ 数字卡片 ═══════════ --&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;ab-stats&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;ab-stat-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;ab-stat-num&#34;&gt;13+&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;ab-stat-label&#34;&gt;Years Experience&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;ab-stat-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;ab-stat-num&#34;&gt;800+&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;ab-stat-label&#34;&gt;Skilled Staff&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;ab-stat-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;ab-stat-num&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;ab-stat-label&#34;&gt;Factories&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;ab-stat-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;ab-stat-num&#34;&gt;70+&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;ab-stat-label&#34;&gt;New Designs / Month&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- ═══════════ 品牌客户墙 ═══════════ --&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;ab-section&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h2 class=&#34;ab-sec-title&#34;&gt;Trusted by Global Brands&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;ab-sec-desc&#34;&gt;Our manufacturing capabilities have been trusted by leading international fashion brands.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;ab-brands&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span&gt;Alpinestars&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span&gt;Topologie&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span&gt;LeSportsac&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span&gt;PINKO&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span&gt;Telfar&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span&gt;Patrizia Pepe&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span&gt;MaxMara&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span&gt;Borbonese&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- ═══════════ 认证 ═══════════ --&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;ab-section ab-section-alt&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h2 class=&#34;ab-sec-title&#34;&gt;International Certifications&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;ab-certs&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;ab-cert&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BSCI&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Social Compliance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;ab-cert&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ISO 9001&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Quality Management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;ab-cert&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GRS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Global Recycled Standard&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;ab-cert&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Intertek&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Product Testing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;ab-cert&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Disney&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Certified Factory&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- ═══════════ 工厂画廊 ═══════════ --&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;ab-section&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h2 class=&#34;ab-sec-title&#34;&gt;Inside Our Facilities&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;ab-gallery&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;figure class=&#34;ab-gallery-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:8080/img/showroom.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Design Center &amp; Showroom&#34; /&gt;&#xA;      &lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;        &lt;strong&gt;Design Center &amp; Showroom&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;        A creative studio where our 18-person team develops 70+ new styles monthly.&#xA;      &lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;    &lt;figure class=&#34;ab-gallery-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:8080/img/cutting-workshop.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Cutting Workshop&#34; /&gt;&#xA;      &lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;        &lt;strong&gt;Cutting Workshop&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;        Precision cutting with industrial-grade machinery for exact specifications.&#xA;      &lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;    &lt;figure class=&#34;ab-gallery-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:8080/img/assembly-workshop.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Assembly Line&#34; /&gt;&#xA;      &lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;        &lt;strong&gt;Assembly &amp; Production&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;        Skilled artisans across multiple stations. 30K–100K units per style.&#xA;      &lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;    &lt;figure class=&#34;ab-gallery-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:8080/img/sample-room.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Sample Showroom&#34; /&gt;&#xA;      &lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;        &lt;strong&gt;Sample Showroom&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;        Hundreds of finished samples — explore materials, colors, and craftsmanship.&#xA;      &lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- ═══════════ OEM / ODM CTA ═══════════ --&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;ab-section ab-section-cta&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h2 class=&#34;ab-sec-title&#34;&gt;Customize Your Order&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p&gt;Full OEM / ODM services — logo embossing, custom hardware, Pantone-matched colors, and premium materials from genuine leather to suede.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>Contact Us</title>
				<link>http://localhost:8080/contact/</link>
				<pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:8080/contact/</guid>
				<description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;get-in-touch&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Get in Touch &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#get-in-touch&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you&amp;rsquo;re looking to place a wholesale order, request samples, or start a custom OEM project — we&amp;rsquo;re ready to help.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Response time: within 24 hours&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;send-an-inquiry&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Send an Inquiry &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#send-an-inquiry&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;inquiry-form&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;form action=&#34;https://formspree.io/f/mbdvbqdd&#34; method=&#34;POST&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;input type=&#34;text&#34; name=&#34;name&#34; placeholder=&#34;Your Name / Company Name&#34; required /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;input type=&#34;email&#34; name=&#34;email&#34; placeholder=&#34;Email Address&#34; required /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;input type=&#34;tel&#34; name=&#34;phone&#34; placeholder=&#34;Phone / WhatsApp Number&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;select name=&#34;inquiry_type&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;option value=&#34;&#34;&gt;— Select Inquiry Type —&lt;/option&gt;&#xA;    &lt;option value=&#34;wholesale&#34;&gt;Wholesale Order&lt;/option&gt;&#xA;    &lt;option value=&#34;oem&#34;&gt;OEM / Custom Order&lt;/option&gt;&#xA;    &lt;option value=&#34;sample&#34;&gt;Sample Request&lt;/option&gt;&#xA;    &lt;option value=&#34;other&#34;&gt;Other&lt;/option&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/select&gt;&#xA;  &lt;textarea name=&#34;message&#34; placeholder=&#34;Tell us about your needs: product style, quantity, customization requirements...&#34;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button type=&#34;submit&#34;&gt;Send Inquiry →&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;&lt;/form&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;direct-contact&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Direct Contact &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#direct-contact&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;thead&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;th&gt;Channel&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;th&gt;Details&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wholesale &amp;amp; OEM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;mailto:info@sensiblebag.com&#34;&gt;info@sensiblebag.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Media &amp;amp; Press&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;mailto:press@sensiblebag.com&#34;&gt;press@sensiblebag.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;General&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;mailto:hello@sensiblebag.com&#34;&gt;hello@sensiblebag.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WhatsApp&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;td&gt;+86 XXX XXXX XXXX&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;follow-us&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Follow Us &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#follow-us&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://instagram.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://pinterest.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Pinterest&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We ship worldwide. Factories located in Dongguan, China and Cambodia.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>Our Process</title>
				<link>http://localhost:8080/craftsmanship/</link>
				<pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:8080/craftsmanship/</guid>
				<description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;from-sketch-to-your-hands&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;From Sketch to Your Hands &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#from-sketch-to-your-hands&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every Sensible Bag goes through a meticulous process — because quality is in the details.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;  &#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:8080/img/process.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Production Process&#34; class=&#34;mx-auto my-0 rounded-md&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;our-commitment-to-quality&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Our Commitment to Quality &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#our-commitment-to-quality&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design&lt;/strong&gt; — Every bag starts with a purpose. Form follows function.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Material Selection&lt;/strong&gt; — We source premium fabrics and hardware that stand the test of time.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Craftsmanship&lt;/strong&gt; — Skilled artisans bring each design to life with precision and care.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quality Control&lt;/strong&gt; — Every piece is inspected before it reaches you.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:8080/collection/&#34;&gt;Explore Our Collection →&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
